snippet.title: TorqueL on PC & PS4! [PLAYISM]
snippet.description:
http://playism-games.com/game/198/torquel
https://store.playstation.com/#!/en-us/games/torquel/cid=UP0969-CUSA02129_00-0000000000000000

Torque up! Hat on!

Roll, tumble and extend to get over magma, high walls, and myriad other obstacles in this puzzle game.

TorqueL is a unique 2D 'rolling' & 'extend' platformer/action/puzzle game. Including a total of 50 chambers, and 7 basic routes.

Can you discover it all?
